flowchart LR
  Subject[Subject] -->|request action on resource| PEP[Policy Enforcement Point]
  PEP --> PDP[Policy Decision Point]
  PDP --> PAP[(Policy Administration Point)]
  PDP --> PIP[(Policy Information Point)]
  PDP -->|permit / deny / challenge / redact| PEP
  PEP -->|permitted action| Resource[(Protected Resource)]
  PEP --> Audit[(Security Audit Log)]
